  <brief_title>A Study With Health Educational Material on Health Promotion in Cancer Survivors</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial on the Effect of Intervention With Health Educational Material on Knowledge, Attitude, and Behavior in Cancer Survivors</official_title>
